<P>

<a href="Research1Intro.html"><font color="#ff3300">Research Part 1: Introduction<font color="#999999"></a>
<P>
<a href="Research2Paleo.html"><font color="#336699">Research Part 2: Paleocortical precursors<font color="#999999"></a>
